<p class="ql-align-center">不久前在网上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流传着<strong>考古界の四大奇事</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201012/1c0b4b3246324b3f834ea8130695c96a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201012/d94719a4f00b4a7fa1abaf6e12b7cf15.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
