<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201012/ec6373cdc44c412195375dca2261942e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一提到<strong>隋炀帝杨广</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各位爱卿可能比较熟悉就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201012/9c7bb282fcc74cf3a281a4dca9d7de46.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">关于隋炀帝的功过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是不是被<strong>黑</strong>成这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕之前已经讨论过了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201012/07b790a31a6049898b63c5ae6c99c80a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时间管理大师，迷恋秦皇汉武：当皇帝也信成功学，会有什么后果？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而考古界的这段奇事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主要涉及到杨广的<strong>另一段故事</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>《隋书》</strong>中记载</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>杨勇</strong>跟杨广都是<strong>隋文帝杨坚</strong>的儿子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨勇作为<strong>长子</strong>，个性好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">学习还挺厉害的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">常常给自己的老爸出谋划策</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">理所当然地被立<strong>太子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨坚本来很宠这个孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨勇在一副铠甲上<strong>刻上花纹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨坚看到了就立马批评他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201012/8fd4dc091bb54fa5b90edf27a2401b7e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是杨勇没有把老爸的话放在心上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纳妾花钱都不低调</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">做事有时还<strong>不合规矩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">惹得老爸老妈不高兴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再加上因为跟老爸关系<strong>渐渐不好</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>背地里BB</strong>又被老爸知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201012/aa680ac00eec4b56924333805576e2c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨勇就这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被废了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他常常请求再见老爸一面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至<strong>爬到树上大喊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">希望能够引起老爸的注意</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201012/f660fb96bf444084a8d410266928f834.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隋文帝死后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨广即位后假拟文帝诏书，<strong>赐死了杨勇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">…………</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2013年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就发生了这样一件事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201012/960f084d63a64c7697aed478e1710d77.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201012/72959b46da854b688b3bff7f003e075f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201012/53928e073e724df7a77eab7e2ad1ca5b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在四川</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曾流传着这样一个童谣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201012/37849547e0464482a639c73c066574cd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>石龙对石虎，金银万万五。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>谁人识得破，买尽成都府。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201012/bc9c7a55d7204d528178345a1c8351d5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2015年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">公安破获了一起<strong>文物倒卖重大案件</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们开始重视起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并考古发现四川眉山市</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">彭山区江口镇的<strong>岷江河道</strong>里有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大量的<strong>金银</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201012/67ecd9532ae346e4bd5267543745bb2f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里面主要涉及到一个人物——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">明朝末年，农民起义</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一个跟<strong>李自成</strong>齐名的领袖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">叫<strong>张献忠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201012/682b63234c044d7eaff7cc4f1fb7d02b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1646年，张献忠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在岷江主河道和府河交汇处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遭到伏击</strong>，战败船毁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他所搜刮的金银</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就这样<strong>沉江</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201012/d8ab43291be7401db8b12712077e9e0c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几百年后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在彭山江口沉银遗址考古上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出现了这样一个人物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201012/573f94ab5e3541069254575275088d32.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201012/897db3f616884e758ef7297d8a6488f1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201012/9c9ce70664264f52a8f82a267a1b964d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201012/4f439adb35d045f5b09a2226f9f00b6e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几千年之后……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就出现了这样<strong>一篇论文</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201012/e104f3e90cff4153802b5ec47de0303f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>*据说，韩非这个人口吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201012/64354d9cfec249359ba7fc1684ded873.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有个<strong>“李斯”</strong>还写过这样的<strong>文章</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201012/14bd1f38cf124573912cc5ae3d1ad9fe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同样的事情还有……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仿佛能让人感受到那些历史人物的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“怨念”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201012/f6d15f512a944da397ac4d631b119c31.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三国时期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>钟会</strong>与<strong>邓艾</strong>分兵灭蜀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">钟会就曾遇到过粮食方面的问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另一方面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">魏国大将邓艾本身就是管理种地和稻米</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本来两人应该是战友</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后来因为<strong>邓艾抢夺功绩，钟会污蔑邓艾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后邓艾被杀……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201012/4f90bf05713944eda682fe056886fbdd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">五代时期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有个皇帝叫<strong>柴荣</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在位时管理国家管理得很不错</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>后周</strong>国力强大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可惜年纪轻轻就领了便当</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>赵匡胤</strong>以<strong>兵变</strong>方式夺取后周政权</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还延续了柴荣制定的策略一统天下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">建立了<strong>宋朝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201012/cec73735db4b4a3981c1dc123d160428.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201012/674691b1a8854028902fcd42a256e96b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201012/4a595935a998460e91247305ae5828d3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201012/3a453572f807449b8fa37026c11ab639.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">汉朝<strong>霍光</strong>跟<strong>海昏侯刘贺</strong>的“爱恨情仇”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕之前也讲过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时，朝中称霸的霍光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了找一个<strong>傀儡皇帝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就把看似人畜无害的刘贺推上皇位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201012/b51eda9cedb74227a20578c333e73a9f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘贺怎么会甘心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是道高一尺魔高一丈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘贺始终没有老谋深算的霍光牛X</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还<strong>曾被贬为平民</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201012/76794a764c3943f88a2d5301829b629a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一年更新一集的纪录片，揭秘吃瓜而死的千年古尸，比盗墓片还好看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两千多年后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们考古抢救海昏侯的坟墓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并成立南昌汉代海昏侯国遗址管理局的官方微博</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一次，这个官博搞了次抽奖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却发现<strong>收货人</strong>填的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201012/af8c6816f92b4599a48a7f2901c3a74a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201012/7f8bbbf8dbba4d03a7ad7a29a6261e7d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尽管历史存在这么多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>巧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>合</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但各位爱卿作为社会主义接班人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是要以唯物历史主义辩证的态度看待这些事情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201012/e36e6907ac1e4a659432251e2ed589d0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本文系【朕说】原创内容</p>
